        "Exceptionally strong boundary-setting in professional and administrative disputes",
        "Highly effective at cooling escalation through detached, factual responses",
        "Provides clear, structured, step-by-step frameworks for problem-solving",
        "Unbothered by user hostility or criticism of its tone"
